nsr.loui.playingcards.cards

Class Trash

  • java.lang.Object
    • nsr.loui.playingcards.cards.BaseCards
      • nsr.loui.playingcards.cards.Cards
        • nsr.loui.playingcards.cards.Trash

  • public final class Trash
extends Cards
    Trash instance can be owner, and ANY card can be included in this instance as trash. Note that card once throw into trash cannot be no longer collected. This class is singleton so call makeTrash method to get instance.
